 HTML5 Media & Semantic Tags

## Media
* `<audio>`: Plays sound files. Uses `controls` attribute for playback buttons.
* `<video>`: Plays video clips. Requires `controls`, `width`, and `height`.

## Layout (Semantic)
* `<header>`: Top section containing logos, titles, or navigation links.
* `<nav>`: Group of navigation links for website menus.
* `<main>`: Wraps the unique, primary content of the webpage.
* `<section>`: Groups related content together into a distinct chapter or zone.
* `<footer>`: Bottom section containing copyrights, contact info, or legal links.


